profile:
Border Plumbing, Heating & Electrical is a locally owned and operated business in the Kelowna area. 
***
We started this business 20 years ago with the intentions of keeping it small and manageable by taking great pride in the fact that we are a family run business. We do not adhere to big business practices or franchise models as we wish to engage our flexibility and freedom to focus on the quality of our work, not quantity.
***
Our customer base is made up of people of the same belief system – they would rather spend a little more time, care, and money knowing the job is done correctly and having the peace of mind that we are there for them after the sale.
***
Being a customer service based company, we refuse to cut corners. In fact, we do all we can to deliver above and beyond what industry standards require. Going the extra mile is what has set us apart from the masses for which we were rewarded with the 2014 Mid-Size Business of the Year award from the Kelowna Chamber of Commerce.
***
We know Border Plumbing, Heating and Air is just one option out of many you could choose. Give us a chance to earn the right to your business. 
***
1.  FAST PLUMBING, HEATING & AIR SERVICE THROUGHOUT THE OKANAGAN VALLEY

From plumbing repairs to heating and AC system repairs and new installations, with Border you won't be kept waiting.

Our dedicated team of technicians and plumbers are available on call, 24/7.  We'll arrive fast in a fully stocked vehicle with the tools and parts to perform the work quickly.

2.  PROFESSIONAL PLUMBING, HEATING AND COOLING

We employ a skilled and experienced team of technicians able to provide the best solutions and quality workmanship for your installation, repair and maintenance needs. 

3.  SAVE WITH OUR PROMOTIONS & UP-FRONT PRICING

We offer great savings with regular promotional offers along with our competitive pricing.  Plus, stay in control with a per-job price that has been provided to you in advance and stays the same through to completion.

4.  PROFESSIONAL, LICENSED AND INSURED

Border Plumbing Heating & Air is fully licensed and insured for all the plumbing and HVAC work you require, so you know you're in safe hands with us.

5.  FREE ESTIMATES ON NEW HEATING & COOLING EQUIPMENT

If you are looking for a new heating or cooling system, call us for a FREE estimate.

6.  GREAT WARRANTIES

You're assured of quality with our written warranty on all workmanship as well as guidance on choosing systems and equipment with great manufacturer warranties.

7. SERVICE EXCELLENCE
***
You'll find the Border Plumbing Heating & Air team helpful, friendly and willing to go that extra mile to ensure your experience with us is great. Our technicians and plumbers always show care when working inside your home by wearing boot covers and using work mats to keep everything neat and tidy and will clean up before leaving.
***
For fast, efficient, and exceptional plumbing, heating and AC solutions throughout the Okanagan Valley, call and speak with the team at Border Plumbing, Heating & Air today.

profile: Premium Comfort is a full-service professional Plumbing Heating and Air Conditioning company based in Kelowna BC. We service the entire Central Okanagan Valley area which includes Kelowna, Vernon, Lake Country, West Kelowna, Peachland, and Big White. We do both Residential and Commercial service, repair, maintenance, retrofit, new install, renovation and new construction. For 25 years, we have been #1 in offering friendly, high quality workmanship, reliable, trustworthy, and professional service. Our team at Premium Comfort Plumbing Heating and Air Conditioning always goes above and beyond when it comes to customer satisfaction. We are fully knowledgeable of all Fortis, Hydro and Federal Gov't Rebate programs to help save our customers money on their next purchase. We take pride in helping our customers save money on their utility bills with our high-efficiency line of Lennox furnaces, boilers, air conditioners, ductless mini splits, heat pumps, tankless water heaters (Navien), hot water tanks (Rheem), air purification, water treatment systems (Kinetico), fireplaces and so much more.  We are one of the only companies in our region to have our own in-house automated sheet metal fabrication shop that fabricates all our own aluminum ductwork which allows us to control quality (maximizing the airflow design for ultimate heating and cooling comfort during should you be building a home). As a premier Lennox dealer (top 1% nationwide), our attention to detail is second to none, along with deep industry knowledge and years of qualified experience is what helps us stand out from the rest.  Dedicated to 100% customer satisfaction, there is nothing that will be overlooked when working with us as our customer at Premium Comfort Plumbing Heating & Air Conditioning.

profile:
For the comfort you deserve.

Part of Premium Comfort’s commitment to excellence is to provide ongoing education for our technicians. Continual development is how we have brought the most innovative and cost effective installations to residents of Kelowna and Okanagan since 1997.

We believe in offering the very best products to our customers.   Lennox is our brand of choice for our heating and air conditioning equipment.  Lennox’s commitment to offering a top quality product with exceptional customer service and innovative, leading edge technology and best in the industry warranties, is the perfect match for Premium Comfort.  

Our sister company Premium Water Treatment shows the same integrity, and is the exclusive Kinetico dealer in The Okanagan Valley.  

Plumbing, Gas-fitting, and HVAC we can do it all from; new home construction, renovations, fireplaces, in-floor heating, steam showers, tank-less water heaters, and all outdoor living designs including; gas tiki-torches, gas BBQ’s, and so much more. 
Call us for preventative maintenance, after hour’s emergencies. We repair, we replace, and we care.
A locally owned and operated family company, we at Premium Comfort believe in giving back to the community. 

From our family to yours, for the comfort you deserve. Premium Comfort.
